title: 257 - S.T.A.N.K.
description: We make a lot of decisions every day, and with the right energy, we can make every decision, the right decision. The truth is, the energy you give to situations and circumstances in your life is a critical factor to your success. In this episode, the guys speak on how having the right energy, positive attitude, and follow-through can make all the difference in the outcome of decisions.
